573
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:34,290
were neighbors.

574
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:36,690
Regarding Unit 1801 in Building 7 now,

575
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,960
did the tenant specifically ask for it,

576
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,290
or did you recommend it?

577
00:18:39,360 --> 00:18:41,560
We recommended it based on his request.

578
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:44,040
The tenant specifically asked for Building 7.

579
00:18:44,040 --> 00:18:44,760
He said,

580
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,290
"The cheaper, the better."

581
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:47,560
How about this.

582
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:49,800
Please make a copy of all the rental contracts for us.

583
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:50,920
We need to investigate.

584
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,400
Okay.

585
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:53,000
This neighborhood is remote.

586
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,720
Plus, there was a fire last year.

587
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,800
They say the Feng Shui is bad.

588
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,560
Very few people live in the neighborhood.

589
00:18:57,560 --> 00:18:58,720
Especially this building.

590
00:18:58,720 --> 00:19:00,040
There are only a few households.

591
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:01,760
Do you know all the tenants in this building?

592
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:02,490
Pretty much.

593
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,650
Do you remember the tenant in 1501?

594
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:05,680
Mrs. Liu?

595
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:07,480
I remember her very well.

596
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:09,040
When the fire happened last year,

597
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:10,400
it was my first day at work.

598
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:13,520
She saved the people on the 10th and 6th floors in the middle of the night.

599
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:14,760
Everyone else ran away.
